Stacia Napierkowska https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stacia_Napierkowska 0 Stacia Napierkowska (16 September 1891 – 11 May 1945) was a French actress, dancer, and director who worked during the silent film era. She appeared in 86 films between 1908 and 1926. Stacia_Napierkowska ( 16_September_1891 – 11_May_1945 ) was a_French_actress , dancer , and director who worked during the_silent_film_era .
